Item 8.01 Other Events.
On June 29, 2020, Morgan Stanley (the
“Company”) issued a press release regarding
the June 25, 2020 release by the Board of
Governors of the Federal Reserve System of the
results of its 2020 Comprehensive Capital
Analysis and Review and notification regarding
the Company’s Stress Capital Buffer.A copy of
the press release is attached hereto as
Exhibit 99.1 and
incorporated into this Item 8.01 by reference.
